panels.text:
You are Jarv. {pool:jarvMoods:0}

Fifty crossings. The Wastes know your weight by now. The ash remembers.

{pool:jarvIntros:1}

Three years ago, the Grand Dominion shattered.

In the Ashen Wastes, the shatter never stopped.

{pool:priorRunSummaries:0}

And yet — {pool:priorRunOpenings:0}

You push the feeling aside. The Wastes are waiting.

They are always waiting.
